      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior features several noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the paint has begun to fade in some areas. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. While the car starts and runs reliably, the suspension is somewhat stiff and it may soon require routine maintenance for wear items like brakes or tires. This is an honest, functional vehicle for someone looking for basic transportation at an affordable price point.",
