      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been well-loved and cared for. It runs like a dream and is perfect for someone looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s ready for any adventure. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m excited for it to find a great new home! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
