    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available now is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46). At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for precise torque vectoring. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The suspension is fitted with Bilstein B16 adjustable dampers, providing superior lateral stability and optimized roll centers. While the car shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, the powertrain and chassis remain exceptionally tight and responsive.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
