      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my awesome car and it's looking for a brand new home! It's in really solid shape and has been such a reliable companion for all my trips. It drives like a dream and is ready to hit the road with you behind the wheel. If you're looking for a dependable, well-cared-for ride that's ready for its next adventure, this is the one! Shoot me a message if you want to come by and check it out!",
      "price": 32500.0,
